&lt;p&gt;Following the planned retirement of a long-serving Consultant we are seeking a Consultant Psychiatrist in Medical Psychotherapy working in the Barnet Personality Disorders Service covering the London Borough of Barnet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Barnet Personality Disorder Team offers a specialist outpatient assessment and treatment service to people living in the London Borough of Barnet whose difficulties meet criteria for Cluster B personality disorder which includes anti-social, emotionally unstable, narcissistic and histrionic personality disorders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a part time post working 3 days a week (6 PAs) based at Barnet Hospital, Springwell Centre, Wellhouse Lane, EN5 3DJ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;*Strictly no agencies please&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further details please contact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dr Gil Kovac, Medical Lead for Barnet Services&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email: gil.kovac@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
